         Actually, once you hit the hp barrier where you can go down to 50% hp and have vexing heal you up to full without wasting any hp, you're pretty much at the efficiency limit of having extra hps. (regen, however, will always improve efficiency until it overrides AL)  Higher hp is more useful than higher mana in that it allows you to survive better.  Taking two 900 damage HTs is nothing if you have 2500 hp.  Taking two 900 damage HTs when you only have 1400 hp is deadly.</P><P></P><P>Etadanik the Redeemed<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
