         <BLOCKQUOTE id=quote><font size=2 face="Verdana" id=quote>quote:<hr height=1 noshade id=quote><BR>110 mana is useless if you are constantly tapping it back super fast because you cannot hold off for 2 extra mobs while using AL.  It is all about being efficient, and believe it or not, HPs = efficient.<BR><hr height=1 noshade id=quote></BLOCKQUOTE id=quote></font id=quote><font face="Verdana" size=2 id=quote></P><P>Apparently you missed the point of my post which stated that it is not a useless item (would you sneeze at a 110 mana item with 10 MR?) and all depends on the makeup of the rest of your gear. Certainly HP are vital to what we do... but they are often cheaper to come by in slots other than secondary... and I looted my hand. I am constantly swapping gear in and out depending on the situation and what is called for. Often the Hand is in the mix --- plus it looks VERY cool with my Primary claws: Drakkel Wolf Claws :)<BR><BLOCKQUOTE id=quote><font size=2 face="Verdana" id=quote>quote:<hr height=1 noshade id=quote></P><P>The difference 200hps makes is HUGE when it comes to regular solo exp.  I can wait 2 extra mobs before I cast Vexing, and let pet do the rest, all the while staying in AL and gaining back mana.  I keep up with 13 per cycle in the grey including resists and I maintain about 50% mana throughout and never stop to take a break.  Only cast Epic, Funeral Pyre, Shackle of Spirit, and Invoke Fear with the occasional Vexing.  With less hps, I couldnt do 13, and would be vexing alot more.<BR><hr height=1 noshade id=quote></BLOCKQUOTE id=quote></font id=quote><font face="Verdana" size=2 id=quote></P><P>I do the same cycle and never stop pulling - but don't bother with shackle and only cast vexing, invoke fear free from my staff and dooming darkness and 1 cast of exile undead. I finish with full HP and full mana pretty much at the end of each fight. Spectre pet can take a bit of a beating and so can I so I consider shackle a bit of a waste on all but the named mobs - and then only rarely.</P><P><BR>Galim Grimshade<BR>Warlock of Prexus.<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
